text:
@RJCcapital @aleabitoreddit $SIVE didnt "pivot" to CPO

the industry has reached a point where its development, research and scalability has hit an inflection point and SIVERS is a sprocket (albeit smaller one) in its story

their Photonics teams/Acq started devops awhile ago

